posting_body: ['Ashton Bellevue, managed by UDR', '10710 NE 10th Street', 'Bellevue, WA 98004', 'show contact info', 'Ashton Bellevue offers residents remarkable views of classic northwest vistas.', 'On approach, this building speaks for itself and it speaks volumes.', 'Twenty soaring floors of glass and visionary architectural detailing.', 'Glorious views in every direction.', 'Walking distance to all Downtown Bellevue office buildings and shopping centers and a short drive to Redmond, Kirkland, and Downtown Seattle.', 'Spacious, open floor plans.', 'Ashton Bellevue is an environment that stimulates, enthralls, and always feels just like home.', '*Furnished Homes Available*', 'Pricing and specials may vary based on lease terms, move-in date, availability, and is subject to change at any time.', 'Offered prices are for base rent only as other charges, fees, terms, and conditions may apply.', 'Square footage, amenities, and floor plan listed may vary between individual units and are subject to availability.', 'Ashton Bellevue, managed by UDR', '10710 NE 10th Street', 'Bellevue, WA 98004', 'show contact info', 'Quick Question?', 'Text us at', 'show contact info', '.', 'Take A Virtual Tour: <URL>', 'VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'Apartment Features', '* Granite Countertops', '* Extra Storage', '* Pre-wired for internet and cable', '* Stainless Steel Appliances', '* Ceiling Fan', '* Pantry', '* Alarm Activation Available', '* Private Patio or Private Balcony (on select apartments)', '* Central Heat and Air', '* Walk-in Closet', '* Window Coverings', '* Air Conditioning', '* Washer and Dryer in unit', '* Refrigerator, Microwave, Dishwasher & Electric Stove', '* Microwave', '* High Definition Digital Cable Packages Available', '* Garden Tub', '* Wood Floors', '*', 'Dual Master Sinks', '* Furnished Options Available, Call for Pricing']
